column2: Reduce incoming stun, daze, fear, and taunt duration.
<c=@abilitytype>Symbols</c> deal increased damage and charge your Justice passive effect twice as fast.
Deal more damage for each stack of vulnerability on your target.
Increases movement speed above the health threshold. Dagger skills recharge faster if activated while above the health threshold.
A recipe to make an ascended light breather with Berserker (+Power, +Ferocity, and +Precision) stats.
<c=@abilitytype>Legendary Assassin.</c> Dodge backward through the Mists. Remove movement-impairing conditions, and gain fury.
Diessa Plateau: Village of Butcher's Block
A recipe to make an ascended heavy breather with Soldier (+Power, +Vitality, and +Toughness) stats.
<c=@abilitytype>Trick.</c> Spin around, reflecting projectiles and throwing daggers that cripple and bleed nearby foes. You can move while spinning.
Gain increased healing to other allies, based on a percentage of healing power.
You and your pet have a chance to cause bleeding on critical hits.
A winner has knocked down the Mushroom Tyrant King three times!
Summon a Dragon Banner at your objective. This banner provides the wielder access to powerful offensive skills, as well as a break bar.

Double-click to summon this mini to follow you around. Only one mini may be in use at a time.
Combine 3 of this mini with Pile of Crystalline Dust, an Obsidian Shard, and a Gift of Ascension in the Mystic Forge to create a Mini Snuggles.
<c=@abilitytype>Commands</c> apply additional boons around you and gain reduced recharge.
The Mordrem invasion is withdrawing for now.
Dodging removes burning and chilled from nearby allies.
Incoming damage in fractals is reduced by 5%% per stack.
Deal increased damage when your health is above the threshold. Blocking or evading an attack heals you.
<c=@abilitytype>Survival.</c> Use mud to cripple, slow, and immobilize foes.

You and your pet deal increased damage to disabled or movement-impaired foes.
Affected conditions are: Stun, Taunt, Daze, Cripple, Fear, Immobilize and Chilled.

You and your illusions deal increased damage to foes without boons. Disabling a foe removes boons from them.
Disables include stun, daze, knockback, pull, knockdown, sink, float, launch, taunt, and fear.
Dolyaks gain increased health and toughness.
Purchase ingredients from Miyani at the Mystic Forge to craft food and drinks for large groups.
Salvaging ascended weapons has a chance to yield this item.
Blind foes that are struck by <c=@abilitytype>Cry of Frustration</c>.

Obtain a Vinewrath Tendril from the Mordrem Vinewrath boss encounter in the Silverwastes. Trade it to the Frozen Jade Researcher located in the Solid Ocean fractal inside the Fractals of the Mists.
This item only has value as part of a collection.
The healing orbs that you create now grant vigor to allies they affect.
A nearby Pact rally point is under attack!
When a <c=@abilitytype>phantasm</c> becomes a clone, it transfers its boons to you.
Focus skills grant you protection and gain reduced recharge.
Your first attack when entering combat applies vulnerability. This ability is refreshed when you use an elite skill.
